en_406251_0	The Security Force Headquarters - West (SFHQ-West) under the supervision of the Commander, Security Forces - West (SFHQ-West), Major General Mahinda Mudalige organized the conduct of a special lecture on ‘prevention of suicides’ on Wednesday (12) at the SLAGSC auditorium, in the Army Cantonment Panagoda.
en_406251_1	Directorate of Preventive Medicine and Mental Health in the Army under the guidance and direction of Lieutenant General Shavendra Silva, acting Chief of Defence Staff and Commander of the Army accordingly requested the SFHQ-West to conduct this lecture.
en_406251_2	It was attended by 25 Officers and 195 Other Ranks of the SFHQ-West.
en_406251_3	Colonel R.M.M Moneragala, Director of Directorate of Preventive Medicine and Mental Health in the Army delivered this valuable lecture.
en_406251_4	Senior Officers of the Security Force Headquarters - West were present during this occasion.
